@page "/tools/api-map"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Bản đồ API</PageTitle>

<h1 class="h3 mb-2">Bản đồ API → giao diện</h1>
<p class="text-muted small mb-4">
    Tra cứu endpoint <code>api/v1/...</code> và trang Blazor tương ứng.
    <a href="/portal">← Trung tâm</a> ·
    <a href="/tools/api-explorer">API explorer</a> (GET/POST/DELETE tùy ý).
</p>

<div class="table-responsive mb-4">
    <table class="table table-sm table-bordered align-middle">
        <thead class="table-light">
            <tr><th>Nhóm</th><th>Endpoint (tóm tắt)</th><th>Trang / hành động</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="small">
            <tr><td>User</td><td><code>POST .../user/register</code></td><td><a href="/register">Đăng ký</a></td></tr>
            <tr><td>User</td><td><code>POST .../user/login</code></td><td><a href="/login">Đăng nhập</a></td></tr>
            <tr><td>User</td><td><code>refresh-token</code>, <code>logout</code>, <code>GET profile</code></td><td><a href="/account">Tài khoản</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Rooms</td><td><code>GET/POST .../rooms</code>, join, join-by-pin</td><td><a href="/lobby">Sảnh</a>, <a href="/tools/rooms">Phòng (REST)</a></td></tr>
            <tr><td>Rooms</td><td><code>GET .../rooms/&#123;id&#125;</code>, details</td><td>Sảnh / phòng chơi; <a href="/tools/rooms">REST</a></td></tr>
            <tr><td>Rooms</td><td>spectator, leave, delete</td><td><a href="/tools/rooms">Phòng (REST)</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Game</td><td><code>.../game/rooms/&#123;id&#125;/...</code> (start, ready, move, state, end…)</td><td><a href="/tools/game">Game REST</a> · chơi: <a href="/lobby">Sảnh</a> (SignalR)</td></tr>

            <tr><td>Betting</td><td><code>.../Betting/rooms/&#123;id&#125;/...</code></td><td><a href="/tools/betting">Betting</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Room mgmt</td><td>stats, by-status, cleanup, force-close, health, transfer…</td><td><a href="/tools/room-management">Quản lý phòng</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Chat</td><td>global messages, activity-feed, room messages</td><td><a href="/tools/chat">Chat &amp; activity</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Match history</td><td><code>.../match-history/&#123;userId&#125;</code>, <code>.../transactions</code></td><td><a href="/history">Lịch sử</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Dashboard</td><td>stats, recent-games, achievements</td><td><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Profile</td><td><code>.../profile/&#123;userId&#125;</code>, <code>/stats</code>, <code>/history</code></td><td><a href="/me">Hồ sơ</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Points</td><td><code>.../points/current</code>, <code>.../points/&#123;userId&#125;</code></td><td><a href="/me/points">Điểm</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Leaderboard</td><td>full list, top, player rank</td><td><a href="/leaderboard">Bảng xếp hạng</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Players</td><td>player-stats, legacy <code>/players</code>, invite, invitations</td><td><a href="/players">Người chơi</a></td></tr>

            <tr><td>Health</td><td><code>.../health</code> và các nhánh con</td><td><a href="/tools/health">Health</a></td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

<p class="small text-muted mb-0">
    Mọi đường dẫn còn lại có thể thử qua <a href="/tools/api-explorer">API explorer</a> (nhập <code>api/v1/...</code>).
</p>
